{DescAliveFull}{}{You see doctor Troy.}
{Speech 1}{}{Predialogue installations}
{Speech 1 Answer 5}{}{fool}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{-}
{Speech 2}{}{Hello, I'm doctor Troy. How can I help you?}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{What do you do here?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Just passing by, thanks.}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{Doctor, you keep looking at me like that... What's the matter?}
{Speech 2 Answer 6*}{}{Doctor, you keep looking at me like that... What's the matter?}
{Speech 2 Answer 13}{}{Troy, I recall that 9 months ago we were solving a certain "demographic problem"...}
{Speech 2 Answer 12}{}{Doctor, it turned out to be not so scary after all. What was that about a reward?}
{Speech 2 Answer 18}{}{Doctor, I have a matter for you. Only you can help.}
