{Speech 2 Answer 24}{}{I'd like to return to our conversation about the donation...}
{Speech 2 Answer 25}{}{I'd like to return to our conversation about the donation...}
{Speech 2 Answer 26}{}{Troy, I can't find doctor Black, do you know where he is now?}
{Speech 2 Answer 15}{}{Doctor Troy, I'm here about supplies.}
{Speech 2 Answer 30}{}{Doctor, I have a message for you from Painless Johnson.}
{Speech 3}{}{I'm the chief physician of Vault City. I care for all the citizens of Vault City and do everything in my power to keep everyone healthy.}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{I see. Then perhaps we'll talk later.}
{Speech 4}{}{If you ever need my services, you can always find me here.}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Thank you. Goodbye.}
{Speech 5}{}{Coochie-coo.@@Cute, and who let you in here?@@All right, get lost.@@Should I call the guards?@@Hmm. You'd do nicely for experiments.}
{Speech 6}{}{Could you spare me a little of your time? There's an important matter to discuss.}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{Yes, of course. I'm listening.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{No time for that, I've got my own affairs.[exit]}
{Speech 7}{}{You've made quite a good name for yourself in our city, and you seem a reasonable enough person, so I'm counting on your understanding.}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Please, go on.}
{Speech 8}{}{As you may know, for a long time the city's population was increased through artificial insemination. However, the results of the latest tests of the gene material look disheartening. We don't yet know what's wrong, but this method has started to fail. Computer modeling has shown that further use of this technology will lead to inevitable degeneration. The city leadership has made a decision…}
{Speech 8 Answer 9}{}{I'm following your line of thought…}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Didn't understand a thing. I don't even know words like that. I'd better be going....}
{Speech 9}{}{We need to conduct an experiment in direct insemination. But, you see, our society is closed, and many people are genetically related. We need an influx of fresh blood… err… a completely outside person who would take part in the experiment and inseminate the traditional way….}
{Speech 9 Answer 10}{}{Stop-stop-stop. Did I get that right? ARE-YOU-OFFERING-ME-TO-SCREW-A-CITY-WOMAN?}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Some experiments or other. What's all this rubbish mean? Goodbye.}
{Speech 10}{}{[hops on the spot] Good heavens! I wouldn't have put it so crudely, but you've grasped the gist. And not one city woman. Three city women.}
{Speech 10 Answer 11}{}{[dancing about impatiently] How much do I have to pay, doctor?}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{Don't even think about it! I'm not your breeding brahmin! You won't get a single one of my sperm for your stupid experiments! [exit]}
{Speech 11}{}{Come now, this is a cruel experiment that we undertake only for the sake of our future. WE will pay YOU for the moral damage and provide you with medicines.\n	We've done the explanatory work with the population, there should be no obstacles. You may proceed.}
{Speech 11 Answer Exit}{}{Proceeding immediately [exit]}
{Speech 12}{}{Yep, excellent. I'm already aware. We'll carefully monitor the health of these women and the development of the embryos. You can drop by in nine months to learn about the little ones. And here's your reward. Take it, you've earned it.}
{Speech 12 Answer Exit}{}{Glad to help.}
{Speech 13}{}{Ah, there you are. Well, congratulations. Fine, sturdy little ones were born. Ahem. All boys. Hmm… and all of them redheads for some reason… Well, never mind, it doesn't matter. As the father, you could choose names for them.}
{Speech 13 Answer 14}{}{Name them Fidget, Crumb and Nono}
{Speech 13 Answer 14*}{}{Name them Legolas, Gimli and Aragorn}
{Speech 13 Answer 14**}{}{Name them Dunno, Donut and Syrupy}
{Speech 13 Answer 14***}{}{Name them Tyr, Vir and Motsognir}
{Speech 13 Answer 14****}{}{Name them Bitard, Anon and Semyon}
{Speech 14}{}{The devil made me do it… All right, as you say}
{Speech 14 Answer Exit}{}{[exit]}
{Speech 15}{}{What's the matter?}
{Speech 15 Answer 16}{}{My name is @pname@. @sex@|I've arrived|I've arrived| to receive my medical allowance for service!}
{Speech 15 Answer 17}{}{My name is @pname@. @sex@|I've arrived|I've arrived| to receive my medical allowance for service!}
