{Speech 18 Answer Exit}{}{We'll come back to this conversation.}
{Speech 19}{}{A doctor? Well, I'm a doctor. As if you didn't know.}
{Speech 19 Answer 20}{}{No. I'm not making myself clear enough, and you misunderstood me. I need a doctor for permanent work. Not here, but in an entirely different place.}
{Speech 20}{}{Ah, so that's it. Well, that's rather difficult. Good doctors are few. And they're all already occupied, working somewhere.}
{Speech 20 Answer 21}{}{Doctor, please help us. We're ready to make a donation to the medical research fund...for such an occasion.}
{Speech 21}{}{All right then. I'll try to help you. I had a student... A most worthy man. I'll try to talk to him. Drop by in a day. By the way, if you donate 12000 to the scientific research fund, that would be very nice. }
{Speech 21 Answer Exit}{}{Very good. I'll come by tomorrow.}
{Speech 21 Answer Exit*}{}{That's too large a sum for us.}
