{Speech 22 Answer Exit}{}{Oh, no. [Exit]}
{Speech 22 Answer 23}{}{Of course, as we agreed.}
{Speech 23}{}{Good. Here, allow me to introduce - doctor Black! An excellent specialist. Talk to him. If the conditions suit him, he's ready to consider relocating.}
{Speech 23 Answer Exit}{}{Thank you doctor, you've been a great help.}
{Speech 24}{}{Don't be in such a hurry, @pname@. I still need some time, I haven't discussed this matter with the right person. Come back tomorrow.}
{Speech 24 Answer Exit}{}{All right. See you.}
